Pipeline Skeleton
=================

One line description:

    Skeletal application based on a pipeline architecture


Attributions:

	Alexandre Trilla


Development:

    The Pipeline Skeleton intends to provide an adequate ground framework
    to buttress a data processing project without compromising its future
    growth.


Credentials:

